<bibRefCitation author="Becker" box="[405,562,864,890]" pageId="1" pageNumber="535" refString="Becker, T. (1911) Chloropidae. Eine monographische Studie. III. Teil. Die indo-australische Region. Annales historiconaturales musei nationalis hungarici, 9, 35 - 170. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 57903" type="journal article" year="1911">
